340   * Add a new {@link Property} item to the underlying collection.
341   *
342   * @param item

346  public boolean addProp(Property item) {
347    Property value = ObjectUtils.requireNonNull(item, "item cannot be null");

356   * collection.

361   */
362  public boolean removeProp(Property item) {
363    Property value = ObjectUtils.requireNonNull(item, "item cannot be null");
364    return _props != null && _props.remove(value);
365  }
